{"tid":2122299,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼移除《花木蘭》北美上映時間","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T04:01:33.000Z","uid":3747,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e25434a2deae908a9d2e0be6f621ec447bafe8eb","tid":2122299,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fdisney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=5ce856dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133</a><br />\n<br />\n#自稱Asian非Chinese美籍出走內地藝人撐港警暴行演員劉亦菲 主演的Disney真人版《花木蘭》電影因武肺疫情在美國三度延期上映，今日官方確認將電影移出未來上映檔期計劃，未知會否轉到Disney+點播平台上播出及其它地區包括香港會否同樣撤出戲院上映計劃。<br />\n<br />\n《花木蘭》原定3月27日在美國公映更已舉行首映會，但在武肺大爆發下宣布延到7月24日，及後再度延期到8月21日，而今次則正式移出上映計劃。<br />\n<br />\n之前 #內地出逃美籍撐港警劉亦菲 因其撐警言論被各地 網民發起 #BoycottMulan 行動進行杯葛，今次武肺長期封閉戲院加上中美關系緊張影響下退檔，#估計Disney將損失3億美元以上拍攝與宣傳費用！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/587880064709339/posts/1622226197941382/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F587880064709339%2Fposts%2F1622226197941382%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=78e6e7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/587880064709339/posts/1622226197941382/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b770d65497305bb70d75cc7f117cc091e6ec83fe","tid":2122299,"uid":119135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔好喺441播呀 <br />\nCut 撚埋佢㗎"},{"pid":"cd6c47c0456b619d3590c983c9e3dc7672459567","tid":2122299,"uid":49044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"PS, 原來鬼國都應該上唔到！<br />